-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COSD - Computes the degree cosinus function
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Argument(s): 1, Real 
   Result type: Real 
   See also   : COS
   Category   : Math functions

   Example: 
     C:> ASET -p X := COSD(90)
     X=0


