COSH - Computes the cosinus hyperbolicus function
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Argument(s): 1, Real 
   Result type: Real 
   Category   : Math functions

   Example: 
     C:> ASET -p X := COSH(1)
     X=1.543081


